data.description: Welcome to this stunning 3-bed, 2-bath gem. With a new roof in 2020, this home offers both style & peace of mind. In desirable South Crestview, enjoy a shorter commute to nearby military bases, making your daily life more convenient. Step inside to laminate floors throughout the open & spacious living area offering a comfortable flow. Enjoy your master retreat featuring a separate shower with large soaking tub, double vanity, separate water closet and huge walk in closet. But the real charm lies outside, a large deck, hot tub, & screened patio for bug-free relaxation. A lush vegetative buffer offers privacy for the nature enthusiast & a serene backdrop to your daily life. This home is adorable & truly has it all-beauty, function and location. Don't miss your chance to make it your own! The kitchen offers a large wrap around breakfast bar for additional seating, great for entertaining. It also features stainless appliances and pantry. Enjoy your master retreat which features a separate shower with large soaking tub, double vanity, separate water closet and a huge walk in closet.  Be sure to check out the spacious laundry room as you enter the home from your attached 2 car garage with opener.  This home is adorable and has so much to offer. You must see it to appreciate it.
